<a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Do you hold a current Environmental Permitting Regulations (EPR) authorisation for any activity being carried out in the facility?</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span></span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><dd govuksummarylistrowactions="" class="govuk-summary-list__actions"><a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Authorisation number</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span></span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><dd govuksummarylistrowactions="" class="govuk-summary-list__actions"><a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Regulator name</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><span></span><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--><!--container--></dd><dd govuksummarylistrowactions="" class="govuk-summary-list__actions"><a class="govuk-link" href="/?change=true">Change</a></dd><!--container--><!--container--></div><div govuksummarylistrow="" class="govuk-summary-list__row"><dt govuksummarylistrowkey="" class="govuk-summary-list__key">Attach a copy of the permit</dt><dd govuksummarylistrowvalue="" class="govuk-summary-list__value"><span>No files provided</span><!--container--><!--con